                        </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                 <div class="card-container margin">
                   <div class="twocard">
                       <div class="image">
                         <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(7).png"></amp-img>
                       </div>
                       <div class="action">
                           <p><strong>15.</strong> Halten Sie jetzt das Profil gedrückt um es umzubenennen.</p>
                       </div>
                   </div>
                   <div class="twocard">
                       <div class="image">
                         <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(8).png"></amp-img>
                       </div>
                       <div class="action">
                           <p><strong>16.</strong> Lassen Sie uns das Profil Pos Day benennen.</p>
                       </div>
                   </div>
                 </div>

                <div class="card-container margin">
                  <div class="twocard">
                      <div class="image">
                        <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(9).png"></amp-img>
                      </div>
                      <div class="action">
                          <p><strong>17.</strong> Danach drücken wir erneut das + um unser letztes Time Profil anzulegen.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="twocard">
                      <div class="image">
                        <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(10).png"></amp-img>
                      </div>
                      <div class="action">
                          <p><strong>18.</strong> Wählen Sie 18:00 Uhr als Trigger für die Nacht-Position.</p>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

               <div class="card-container margin">
                 <div class="twocard">
                     <div class="image">
                       <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(9).png"></amp-img>
                     </div>
                     <div class="action">
                         <p><strong>19.</strong> Weisen Sie dem Profil den goTo2 Task zu.</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
                 <div class="twocard">
                     <div class="image">
                       <amp-img class="shadow" noloading height=768 width=432 layout=responsive src="/images/Advanced_User/Tasker_Timer_(10).png"></amp-img>
                     </div>
                     <div class="action">
                         <p><strong>20.</strong> Und benennen Sie dieses Profil auf Pos Night um.</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
